#: ../../docs/user_manual/plugins/core_plugins/plugins_offline_editing.rst:5
msgid "Offline Editing Plugin"
msgstr "Dodatak za oflajn uređivanje"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/plugins/core_plugins/plugins_offline_editing.rst:7
msgid ""
"For data collection, it is a common situation to work with a laptop or a "
"cell phone offline in the field. Upon returning to the network, the changes "
"need to be synchronized with the master datasource (e.g., a PostgreSQL "
"database). If several persons are working simultaneously on the same "
"datasets, it is difficult to merge the edits by hand, even if people don’t "
"change the same features."
msgstr ""
"Za prikupljanje podataka, uobičajena je situacija rad sa laptopom ili "
"mobilnim telefonom oflajn na terenu. Po povratku u mrežu, izmene je potrebno"
" sinhronizovati sa glavnim izvorom podataka (npr. PostgreSQL bazom "
"podataka). Ako više osoba istovremeno radi na istim skupovima podataka, "
"teško je ručno spojiti izmene, čak i ako ljudi ne menjaju iste objekte."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/plugins/core_plugins/plugins_offline_editing.rst:13
msgid ""
"The |offlineEditingCopy| :sup:`Offline Editing` Plugin automates the "
"synchronisation by copying the content of the datasource to a SpatiaLite or "
"GeoPackage database and storing the offline edits to dedicated tables. After"
" being connected to the network again, it is possible to apply the offline "
"edits to the master dataset."
msgstr ""
"Dodatak |offlineEditingCopy| :sup:`Oflajn uređivanje` automatizuje "
"sinhronizaciju kopiranjem sadržaja izvora podataka u SpatiaLite ili "
"GeoPackage bazu podataka i čuvanjem oflajn izmena u za to namenjene tabele. "
"Nakon ponovnog povezivanja na mrežu, moguće je primeniti oflajn izmene na "
"glavni skup podataka."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/plugins/core_plugins/plugins_offline_editing.rst:77
msgid "offlineEditingCopy"
msgstr "offlineEditingCopy"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/plugins/core_plugins/plugins_offline_editing.rst:19
msgid "To use the plugin:"
msgstr "Da biste koristili dodatak:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/plugins/core_plugins/plugins_offline_editing.rst:21
msgid ""
"Open a project with some vector layers (e.g., from an Esri Shapefile, "
"PostgreSQL or WFS-T datasource)."
msgstr ""
"Otvorite projekat sa nekim vektorskim slojevima (npr. iz Esri Shapefile, "
"PostgreSQL ili WFS-T izvora podataka)."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/plugins/core_plugins/plugins_offline_editing.rst:23
msgid ""
"Assuming you have already enabled the plugin (see "
":ref:`core_and_external_plugins`) go to :menuselection:`Database --> Offline"
" Editing -->` |offlineEditingCopy| :guilabel:`Convert to offline project`. "
"The eponym dialog opens."
msgstr ""
"Pod pretpostavkom da ste već omogućili dodatak (pogledajte "
":ref:`core_and_external_plugins`) idite na :menuselection:`Baza podataka -->"
" Oflajn uređivanje -->` |offlineEditingCopy| :guilabel:`Pretvori u oflajn "
"projekat`. Otvara se istoimeni dijalog."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/plugins/core_plugins/plugins_offline_editing.rst:26
msgid ""
"Select the :guilabel:`Storage type`. It can be of :guilabel:`GeoPackage` or "
":guilabel:`SpatiaLite` database type."
msgstr ""
"Izaberite :guilabel:`Tip skladišta`. Može biti tipa baze podataka "
":guilabel:`GeoPackage` ili :guilabel:`SpatiaLite`."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/plugins/core_plugins/plugins_offline_editing.rst:28
msgid ""
"Use the :guilabel:`Browse` button to indicate the location of the database "
"in which to store the :guilabel:`Offline data`. It can be an existing file "
"or one to create."
msgstr ""
"Koristite dugme :guilabel:`Pregledaj` da biste naznačili lokaciju baze "
"podataka u kojoj će se čuvati :guilabel:`Oflajn podaci`. To može biti "
"postojeća datoteka ili ona koju treba napraviti."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/plugins/core_plugins/plugins_offline_editing.rst:31
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Select remote layers` section, check the layers you'd like"
" to save. The content of the layers is saved to database tables."
msgstr ""
"U odeljku :guilabel:`Izaberi udaljene slojeve` označite slojeve koje biste "
"želeli da sačuvate. Sadržaj slojeva se čuva u tabele baze podataka."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/plugins/core_plugins/plugins_offline_editing.rst:35
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Since target database formats do not have native list support, the offline "
"editing plugin transforms {string, number} list fields into string fields "
"where values are separated by commas. This allows reading and edit of the "
"contents of those fields when offline."
msgstr ""
"Pošto ciljni formati baza podataka nemaju nativnu podršku za liste, dodatak "
"za oflajn uređivanje transformiše {niska, broj} polja liste u niskovna polja"
" gde su vrednosti razdvojene zarezima. Ovo omogućava čitanje i uređivanje "
"sadržaja tih polja kada ste oflajn."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/plugins/core_plugins/plugins_offline_editing.rst:40
msgid ""
"If you would like to handle both the field from the original layer and the "
"offline layer, you can rely on the :ref:`try() "
"<expression_function_Conditionals_try>` and :ref:`array <array_functions>` "
"expression functions, e.g.::"
msgstr ""
"Ako biste želeli da rukujete i poljem iz originalnog sloja i oflajn sloja, "
"možete se osloniti na funkcije izraza :ref:`try() "
"<expression_function_Conditionals_try>` i :ref:`array <array_functions>`, "
"npr.::"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/plugins/core_plugins/plugins_offline_editing.rst:46
msgid ""
"You can check |checkbox| :guilabel:`Only synchronize selected features if a "
"selection is present` allowing to only save and work on a subset. It can be "
"invaluable in case of large layers."
msgstr ""
"Možete označiti |checkbox| :guilabel:`Sinhronizuj samo izabrane objekte ako "
"je izbor prisutan` čime se omogućava čuvanje i rad samo na podskupu. To može"
" biti neprocenjivo u slučaju velikih slojeva."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/plugins/core_plugins/plugins_offline_editing.rst:73
msgid "checkbox"
msgstr "checkbox"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/plugins/core_plugins/plugins_offline_editing.rst:50
msgid "This is all!"
msgstr "To je sve!"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/plugins/core_plugins/plugins_offline_editing.rst:51
msgid "Save your project and bring it on the field."
msgstr "Sačuvajte svoj projekat i ponesite ga na teren."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/plugins/core_plugins/plugins_offline_editing.rst:52
msgid "Edit the layers offline."
msgstr "Uredite slojeve oflajn."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/plugins/core_plugins/plugins_offline_editing.rst:53
msgid ""
"After being connected again, upload the changes using "
":menuselection:`Database --> Offline Editing -->` |offlineEditingSync| "
":guilabel:`Synchronize`."
msgstr ""
"Nakon ponovnog povezivanja, otpremite izmene pomoću :menuselection:`Baza "
"podataka --> Oflajn uređivanje -->` |offlineEditingSync| "
":guilabel:`Sinhronizuj`."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/plugins/core_plugins/plugins_offline_editing.rst:79
msgid "offlineEditingSync"
msgstr "offlineEditingSync"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/plugins/core_plugins/plugins_offline_editing.rst:56
msgid ""
"Layers that are used offline are marked with the |indicatorOffline| icon in "
"the :guilabel:`Layers` panel."
msgstr ""
"Slojevi koji se koriste oflajn označeni su ikonom |indicatorOffline| u "
"panelu :guilabel:`Slojevi`."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/plugins/core_plugins/plugins_offline_editing.rst:75
msgid "indicatorOffline"
msgstr "indicatorOffline"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/plugins/core_plugins/plugins_offline_editing.rst:64
msgid "Create an offline project"
msgstr "Napravi oflajn projekat"
